{
  "stem": "1222.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Two miles, the same steps, the same thing, we stopped even when the ditches where they threw the dead.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was my wish-- to the grave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "These Ukrainian people, they walk with bouquets of flowers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were crying more than me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They kissed the ground.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I wouldn't call these people they were killers, because these people, they walked more slow than they were my age.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe their parents-- it was some of the elderly people walking too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I wouldn't swear for them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But these people were walking up to today.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then later on, they start screaming to the man, they should let me into that house to look because my grandfather was born.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they screamed that, give him back the house!",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's his house!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the man got sterilized.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "First, he didn't want let me in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He let me in and he started shaking, an elderly man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I told him I said, I not-- didn't come to take away the house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I came around to see.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I looked in that garden, what my mother had me-- we didn't have such a thing like a hospital.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother used to tell me many times for a joke, when I didn't listen to her, she says, Shmuelik, I should have left you in that-- that garden.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why would I pick you up?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had you there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I looked up in that, when I looked up at that beautiful trees, [SOBBING] that beautiful apple wood, I grew up there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It broke my heart.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I took a taxi with my two children, who went there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And first of all, I was thinking to take a policeman.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said to my children, no, I am not taking a policeman.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
